      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0011"/><hi rend="latintype">Rohr-</hi><hi rend="pre-print">Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tkarte</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Hotel</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><subst><del rend="strikethrough"><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb127">B<unclear>ri</unclear>st<unclear>o</unclear>l</rs></hi></del><add place="below"><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb399">Continental</rs></hi></add></subst></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0012"/><date when="1905-11-20">Montag</date>. <salute>Lieber Freund,</salute>
               Es hat mir<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr leid gethan, Deinen lieben Be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>uch <date when="1905-11-19">ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern</date> ver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>äumt zu haben. Ich muß wenige Minuten vorher weggegangen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein.
               Hätte<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du mir telephonirt,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o hätte ich Dich gern erwartet.</p><p>Will<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du <date when="1905-11-20">heut</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time> mit mir in die <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03237-1"/><rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb145351">Oper</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03237-1"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> verbrachte den <time>Abend</time>
                  nicht mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs>, sondern mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11813">Siegfried Jacobsohn</rs>. <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1905-11-20" subtype="See"/>.</note> gehen
                  (<hi rend="latintype"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb32011">Fidelio</rs></hi>, Urfa<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ung)? Bis <time>4 Uhr</time> halte ich das Billet zu Deiner Verfügung.
               Erbitte telephoni<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>che Antwort.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <lb/>Dein <signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
